## ðŸ“‹ System Requirements Verification

### Before Installation
```bash
# Check Python version
python --version  # Should be 3.8+

# Check pip
pip --version

# Check available disk space
df -h  # Linux/macOS
Get-Volume  # Windows

# Check RAM
cat /proc/meminfo  # Linux
free -h  # macOS
```

### After Installation
```bash
# Test all imports
python -c "import cv2, tensorflow, sklearn; print('âœ“ All OK')"

# Test GPU (if applicable)
python -c "import tensorflow as tf; print(tf.config.list_physical_devices('GPU'))"

# Run sample detection
python main.py --source video_file --path data/sample_video.mp4
```

